    <!-- About Text -->
    <string name="about_text">VA Trout Spotter is a mobile app designed to help anglers track and find trout stocking information in Virginia waters.\n\nThe app provides up-to-date information on trout stocking locations, dates, and details to enhance your fishing experience in Virginia.\n\nVA Trout Spotter is open source software. You can view the source code, report issues, or contribute to the project on GitHub:\nhttps://github.com/kenkeremath/va-trout-spotter\n\nHappy fishing!</string>

    <!-- Disclaimer Text -->
    <string name="disclaimer_text">VA Trout Spotter is not affiliated with, endorsed by, or connected to any government agency, including the Virginia Department of Wildlife Resources (DWR).\n\nThe app accesses publicly available data from the Virginia DWR website to provide trout stocking information, but it is an independent application developed by a third party.\n\nAll trout stocking data is sourced from public information provided by the Virginia DWR. For official information, please visit the Virginia DWR website directly.</string>

